{"tid":764974,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本兔兔島: 大久野島🐰😊+兔仔傷心 憂愁【身體語言】","createTime":"2018-08-02T11:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T15:09:15.000Z","uid":197098,"like":41,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d38f9b4012efec9cb7eacdeee02ee542e2e02106","tid":764974,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家有沒有去過日本「兔兔島」大久野島？是兔迷必去的地方！有1000多隻自由自在地兔子活在這裡。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLF7jueXt6oU&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=82b9be03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU</a><br />\n<br />\n但是其實島內的兔仔有很多活得不開心和不長壽，雖然沒有捕食者(predatory animals)的威脅，但是牠們很多有生病的、沒有足夠糧食及營養。所以兔迷下次去最好帶牧草, 例如: Timothy Hay, Oat Hay, Orchard Hay等等，給牠們最基本的糧食，高纖維。不要給高糖份的和零食，例如: 蘿蔔和水果。當兔子耳朵平放在後面、耳口向下、坐姿躺下/蹲下就代表牠們不開心，耳朵越後就越憂愁。以下video 可看到大久野島兔仔憂愁的時候:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNdKKWbp7U_k&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=650d8ed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k</a> <br />\n<br />\n另一個video 看到兔子憂愁，耳朵越後就越不開心，主人就真的要看看究竟做錯什麼事，牠亦可能生病了:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xfQUCe7kp8&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=59d100e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>注意:</strong> 這與驚慌(耳朵平放在後面、耳口向側、坐姿蹲下）和憤怒（耳朵和驚慌一樣，但站起來很硬對住你）很不同。一個舒適的兔仔會躺下、手腳伸展出來 。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>領養兔仔：</ins></strong><a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3fb51a32\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a><br />\n<strong>更多關於兔子憂愁的身體語言：</strong><a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Falas-woe-is-me%2F%20&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c3ec6af3\" target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/ </a></span>"},{"pid":"110692f262d8388b490a8f99837c421b25d87959","tid":764974,"uid":41368,"like":18,"dislike":37,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"突然好想食兔肉"},{"pid":"a5245e5e5c40a3ed1dd3dfb04bbb832357824918","tid":764974,"uid":25560,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"110692f262d8388b490a8f99837c421b25d87959","tid":764974,"uid":41368,"like":18,"dislike":37,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"突然好想食兔肉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"食囉，大型超市有售"},{"pid":"c413e51d39d3e2d329d36485d5b714f6ca6b1d4c","tid":764974,"uid":74214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T20:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c5403379d627cc1de06b804a70c95f6e1df4a8","tid":764974,"uid":197098,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:33:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【身體語言】兔仔開心到極!! +室內養會長壽!</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。當牠們binky 時，這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。兔子在室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有任何天氣和敵人威脅，感到平靜和舒適。以下2個videos 可以看到兔子最開心的時候：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE90ikFGQTqs&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3dcc16af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FDMWC5U0gkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFDMWC5U0gkw&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=fe7be56f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FDMWC5U0gkw</a> <br />\n<strong>兔子高難度技能: 打鼓, 簽名, 打籃球:</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dLCEU3baplk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdLCEU3baplk&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=27fae2c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dLCEU3baplk</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>領養兔仔：</strong></ins><a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3fb51a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a><br />\n兔子深入資訊：<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=702d66c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a></span>"},{"pid":"b6caf4838af0085ac1562afa7cd29aef920832d6","tid":764974,"uid":79353,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:34:46.000Z","msg":"連登首席兔仔瘋狂fans club會長<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad3baccff693cfe54913be5fa20a67e9e8c566d","tid":764974,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:35:09.000Z","msg":"🐰🐇🐰🐇🐰🐇"},{"pid":"c6b17c2970fb762c5dadc3c4305809606b5f562a","tid":764974,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6caf4838af0085ac1562afa7cd29aef920832d6","tid":764974,"uid":79353,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:34:46.000Z","msg":"連登首席兔仔瘋狂fans club會長<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"哈哈"},{"pid":"1cf3c43592209a897c39cef06896cbae22e42716","tid":764974,"uid":34001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:00:29.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b096cf20b72d84f687f7872f510e20219221f8b2","tid":764974,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">怎樣可以簡單地訓練兔仔去廁所？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">訓練兔仔🐰去廁所是很簡單的。糞便是沒有臭味的，而且是乾的，所以通常可以拿上來放回兔子的廁所（牠們便會知道要去廁所大小便）然後洗手。尿有時會有少少味，最好把白醋加水放入噴霧樽，然後清洗地板，這樣的話會立刻清除味道及減少牠們在這裏小便。<br />\n以下3個videos 有教, 步驟簡單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zsB7SILsOns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzsB7SILsOns&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e79d3782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zsB7SILsOns</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gP4IaOQsKl4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgP4IaOQsKl4&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=dca3a359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gP4IaOQsKl4</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GHRkf5z6EQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0GHRkf5z6EQ&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=98a1678d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GHRkf5z6EQ</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>領養兔仔</strong>：<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3fb51a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a> <br />\n兔子深入資訊：<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=702d66c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a> </span>"},{"pid":"7b5650a8039805bbcbe3e95d96f591cc95e62ad0","tid":764974,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>狗狗搶野食! 兔兔毫無還手之力! 🙈🙈</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔仔是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animal)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。當牠們側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。(你可想像正前方是盲點，側面才看得最清楚，前腳移動有限，又怎會攻擊到他人？）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video 可看到狗狗搶吃兔糧, 兔兔毫無還手之力😭😆🙈:</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJKwW65LcLIg&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=266d9d02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg</a><br />\nhahaha"},{"pid":"66d2f1eb1b629b0f4ca0012b40d847c644265c60","tid":764974,"uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T03:52:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">領養兔仔，不要買！🐰🐰😊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會領養，這裏有太多兔子正在等新主人帶牠們去新的家，過新的生活。詳情可去<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3fb51a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a> <br />\n<br />\n兔子親吻主人，這是代表你是一個好主人，以下2個videos 可看到： <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMaovq8Vz1LM&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0ce722c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Maovq8Vz1LM</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpyL0yEs-ka8&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=536bd74e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>兔子高難度技能 - 打鼓、打籃球、簽名: 🐰🐰😊</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dLCEU3baplk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdLCEU3baplk&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=27fae2c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dLCEU3baplk</a></span>"},{"pid":"284cd793d1318579361febf59d176f597ca301f9","tid":764974,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撫摸兔仔很重要! 增加自尊心!</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">在大自然內，兔仔有牠們的等級制度。一個高級(dominant)的兔仔會groom (舔和梳理) 一個次級(inferior)的兔仔。但高級的亦會要求次級的兔仔groom 牠，這是一定要服從的。當兔仔低頭向前躺在地上，牠就是想你groom (撫摸和親吻) 牠，這樣可以增加牠的自尊心、令牠舒適、快樂、心理健康。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom牠們，令牠們冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。<br />\n<br />\n兔仔是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animal)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。<strong><ins>兔子喜歡吸引人注意，有時我們看電視的時候，兔子會躺在電視機前面，幸好牠們不知道我們其實不在看牠們。因此，經常陪牠們玩是重要的，兔子是群體性動物，如果主人沒有空，最好領養多一隻兔子陪伴牠。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video是一個等級制度的例子, 可以在0:59 看到：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyv4VhuZv_s&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=99f3523e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s</a> <br />\n<br />\n除了騎着兔子背後，兔子還會躺在另一隻兔子的頸上來顯示牠是比較高層次的(show dominance), 這類行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9WUGogDlg4&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=140014c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>領養兔仔:</ins></strong> <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3fb51a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a> <br />\n兔子深入資訊：<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=702d66c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n關於兔子身體語言(害怕、開心、憂愁、憤怒): <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=a87ed879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a> </span>"},{"pid":"fa575e144e2174aae62830d37b69d69b1ec9d652","tid":764974,"uid":45936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:43:01.000Z","msg":"前幾日去左,<br />\n的確都幾多病病地咁<br />\n有d係單眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8f845ed30d84385ca7eea2aba2256966b504e8","tid":764974,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa575e144e2174aae62830d37b69d69b1ec9d652","tid":764974,"uid":45936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:43:01.000Z","msg":"前幾日去左,<br />\n的確都幾多病病地咁<br />\n有d係單眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:46:26.000Z","msg":"有沒有照片或影片分享？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ea1481b017e029da1b3167f2e22e2e097cff4b","tid":764974,"uid":197958,"like":0,"di