大便都係周圍柯<br />\n係咪要不停執晒佢?"},{"pid":"f64854f57423def2aab5690681ebfb694a0306e2","tid":764974,"uid":30464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a5245e5e5c40a3ed1dd3dfb04bbb832357824918","tid":764974,"uid":25560,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"110692f262d8388b490a8f99837c421b25d87959","tid":764974,"uid":41368,"like":18,"dislike":37,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"突然好想食兔肉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"食囉，大型超市有售"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T01:57:14.000Z","msg":"香港邊間有?<br />\n記得細個食過,好嫩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261d7f46b6a012de32036dfe9fb0db47245bc706","tid":764974,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"兔島嗰d食太多零食搞到唔健康<br />\n當地其實應該賣牧草俾遊客餵而唔係水果生菜蘿蔔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b918e53dd17f201b8285ffcb3949bd43020b57f","tid":764974,"uid":45936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2d5c7f73700b8dadf669d390434a684ce875e6a","tid":764974,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa575e144e2174aae62830d37b69d69b1ec9d652","tid":764974,"uid":45936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:43:01.000Z","msg":"前幾日去左,<br />\n的確都幾多病病地咁<br />\n有d係單眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T17:43:43.000Z","msg":"係咪少左好多遊客?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T02:34:46.000Z","msg":"少唔少就唔知,我都係去過一次,無比較,<br />\n但感覺上都唔算太多人,<br />\n不過可能係同之前大豪雨搞到JR吳線成條唔通,過去果度麻煩左好多有關"},{"pid":"806ec1b62c6d4f3c4cca94394fab84e07e6bfd80","tid":764974,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"261d7f46b6a012de32036dfe9fb0db47245bc706","tid":764974,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"兔島嗰d食太多零食搞到唔健康<br />\n當地其實應該賣牧草俾遊客餵而唔係水果生菜蘿蔔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"我睇日本人都係買蘿蔔去餵,重話遲左去班兔仔會飽到唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991a708022d4190a92eae4ab32df2e4f66463d1b","tid":764974,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d40f9b6151b36df3f860ec585580492e8d4307e","tid":764974,"uid":22590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T01:56:01.000Z","msg":"新手兔奴留名<br />\n佢終於識小便但大便都係周圍柯<br />\n係咪要不停執晒佢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T02:35:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">對，每次牠隨地大便，拍手掌大聲說No, 然後輕輕地帶兔子回到廁所，讓牠知道是不可以的。將隨地的大便放回廁所內，牠便會知道要在這裏去廁所。每次牠在廁所內大小便，就給他零食作獎勵。選擇獎勵，不要懲罰。記住不要打兔子，牠們與狗和貓不同，如果打，牠永遠不會忘記，令到與主人關係和信任差。壓力(stress) 亦可以會令兔子生病。兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(predatory animals)的目標。他們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚。<br />\n<br />\n當然，兔子要絕育才可以訓練去廁所，因為霸地盤(territorial marker), 絕育後會大大減少霸地盤。另外，兔子是很容易患上生殖器疾病的動物，所以絕育會令牠們更健康和長命！<br />\n<br />\n當然，有時候牠們不開心不聽話或者些少霸地盤原因也會隨地大便。</span>"},{"pid":"16d5234c86ee97b3ba33f5a5b1c54263fa83731a","tid":764974,"uid":130225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rabbitsonline.net/proxy.php?image=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.therabbithouse.com%2Fbehaviour%2Fimages%2Feardirection.gif&amp;hash=688b90f1ad88900e8c7520d216f6cb83\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rabbitsonline.net%2Fproxy.php%3Fimage%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.therabbithouse.com%252Fbehaviour%252Fimages%252Feardirection.gif%26hash%3D688b90f1ad88900e8c7520d216f6cb83&h=e8ca53ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"358821155629d85e69d8ad5a9037c0214efea2aa","tid":764974,"uid":45936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"261d7f46b6a012de32036dfe9fb0db47245bc706","tid":764974,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"兔島嗰d食太多零食搞到唔健康<br />\n當地其實應該賣牧草俾遊客餵而唔係水果生菜蘿蔔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi